Content: I have an Honda Cbr 929 2001. It was riding fine the day before. Next morning i went to go for an ride and when i turn the ignition switch on everything was okay until i press the start button and everything shutdown. I checked the fuse box and everything seems okay. I check the battery and it was given me 2.2v and after a few second jump to 12.7v. But when i give it a start the + wire on battery spark and everything shutdown again.
